You have to find the sum of the first x powers of a number n starting from 0. You will find that this puzzle will be easier if you know the trick
Input
n: an integer
x: an integer
Output
The sum of the first x powers of n.
Constraints
x>=1 and n>=1
Example
Input
2
5
Output
31



coding:
n = int(input())
x = int(input())

k = 1
s = 0
for i in range(x):
    s += k
    k *= n
print(s)
